high_descs: Turn around and go past the edge of the counter on the right, then turn right and go past the fridge, then turn right and go to the stove
Pick up the pan from the front right burner
Turn right and go as far as the sink then turn right and go to the fridge
Chill the pan in the fridge, then take the pan out of the fridge
Turn left and go to the far wall then turn right and go to the chair then turn right to face the table
Put the pan on the table to the left of the notepad
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on a kitchen table

high_descs: Turn around and then turn right. Turn right again to find the stove.
Pick up the Pan from the front right burner of the stove.
Carry the pan and turn to the right, then the right again to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pan inside. Shut the door and then open it again. Take out the pan and shut the door.
Hold the pan and turn to the left. Turn to the right and find the round table.
Place the pan on the far left side of the table, in the corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the stove.
Pick up a pot on the stove.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the pot in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Put the pot on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled pot to the round table in the corner.
